name: Work Order Status
query:
SELECT
    Distinct(tabProject.name) as "Project:Link/Project:100",
    tabProject.status as "Status:text:100",
    `tabSO Work Order`.name as "SO:text:90",
    `tabSO Work Order`.expected_ship_date as "Ship Date:date:90"
FROM 
    tabProject, 
    `tabSO Work Order`
WHERE 
    `tabSO Work Order`.project = tabProject.name
ORDER BY tabProject.Name
